<h3>Auto Thumbnail Feature</h3><p>If you turn this feature on (set it to YES) this will make it so you do not have to upload a seperate image for the thumbnails.&nbsp;</p><p>IMPORTANT:&nbsp; Turning this feature on will require the installation of the cfx_image tag on the hosting server.&nbsp; Check with your host provider or website administrator before turning this feature on (For information on installing the custom tag, see the online manual).</p>




